@startuml
title DevLink - Adapter (wzorzec strukturalny)

skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

class "CLI Daemon" as Daemon <<service>> {
  +run_task(client: DevLinkApiClient, task_payload: dict[str, Any]): None
}

interface AgentAdapter <<interface>> {
  +run(task: AgentTask): AsyncIterator<AgentEvent>
}

class CodexAdapter <<adapter>> {
  -stdout_lines: list[str]
  -stderr_lines: list[str]
  -assistant_messages: list[str]
  -edited_files: list[dict[str, Any]]
  +run(task: AgentTask): AsyncIterator<AgentEvent>
}

class ShellAdapter <<adapter>> {
  +run(task: AgentTask): AsyncIterator<AgentEvent>
}

class AgentTask <<dataclass>> {
  +id: str
  +prompt: str
  +project_path: str
  +model: str
  +approval_policy: str
  +tool_settings: dict[str, Any]
}

class AgentEvent <<dataclass>> {
  +event_type: str
  +message: str
  +payload: dict[str, Any]
}

class "Codex CLI process" as CodexProcess <<external>> {
  +command: str = "codex exec --json"
  +stdout: bytes
  +stderr: bytes
  +exit_code: int
}

class "Backend API" as BackendApi <<api>> {
  +post_task_event(task_id: str, event: AgentEvent): TaskEvent
  +finish_task(task_id: str, status: str): Task
}

Daemon --> AgentAdapter : uses common contract
Daemon --> BackendApi : sends AgentEvent

CodexAdapter ..|> AgentAdapter
ShellAdapter ..|> AgentAdapter

CodexAdapter --> CodexProcess : adapts external output
CodexAdapter --> AgentEvent : emits normalized events
ShellAdapter --> AgentEvent : emits normalized events

AgentAdapter --> AgentTask : consumes
AgentAdapter --> AgentEvent : produces

note right of CodexAdapter
Adapter zamienia stdout/stderr
i JSON stream z Codex CLI
na wspolny format AgentEvent.
end note

legend right
  <<service>> logika orkiestracji
  <<interface>> wspolny kontrakt
  <<adapter>> konkretna implementacja
  <<dataclass>> obiekt danych
  <<external>> system zewnetrzny
endlegend

@enduml
